{"tid":1780352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話香港人善忘 同我入黎回憶下612個日發生咩事","createTime":"2019-12-12T09:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T10:56:32.000Z","uid":236124,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa873c688175be1518b83c991dfbbfe4e3519ff","tid":1780352,"uid":236124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:51:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">612 </span><br />\n個日既香港係黑色既 <br />\n當日原訂為《逃犯條例》修訂在立法會進行二讀的日子。<br />\n大量年輕示威者，徹夜留守為求阻止二讀，並且發起三罷 6 12罷工罷課罷市。<br />\n<br />\n有班我地稱為耶L 既基督徒團體 ，連續唱左9個鐘 Sing Hallelujah to the Lord<br />\n礙於宗教集會自由 警方朝早無清到場。<br />\n個日我依然繼續返工，但不停係公司睇新聞同連登<br />\n我無係現場 但我知道在場既人 大部分都係10幾廿歲 ，為左阻止條例通過，佔據夏慤道一帶。<br />\n612下午，警方以催淚彈、橡膠子彈及布袋彈武力清場 ，並定性為暴動。(其後改口)<br />\n個日既新聞片段我好深刻<br />\n有個老師比橡膠子彈擊中右眼 <br />\n係中信大廈附近施放多枚催淚彈 差d人踩人<br />\n有個媽媽手無寸鐵企係一堆有盾牌既警察前面 哭求停止攻擊學生 最後被近距離槍擊<br />\n有女示威者內衣外露被幾個警察抬起  <br />\n<br />\n太多太多 歡迎補充<br />\n從此個日 黑警開始叫黑警 <br />\n 如果你諗起612當日 個心仍然覺得痛覺得嬲 今晚見<br />\n<br />\n12/12「齊上齊落」集會 - 612半週年紀念<br />\n撤回暴動定性 撤銷義士控罪<br />\n<br />\n日期︰2019年12月12日(四)<br />\n時間︰19:00 - 21:00<br />\n地點︰愛丁堡廣場<br />\n主辦︰#民間集會團隊<br />\n*已獲發不反對通知書"},{"pid":"f25b79406d861d1498f70b71651e0a7f860c15e1","tid":1780352,"uid":226594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cb8dd7a504eb9f0dafe89d49e4dbe5f7d589e6","tid":1780352,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"朝早個個買飯團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619b1bdb5354d7897bc5c57d1b7cd09b31c979b1","tid":1780352,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:04:58.000Z","msg":"sorry p牌仔借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男銷售員 6 月涉推跌六旬男子致死被控謀殺　控方近半年仍未能確定死因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n手足無證據都坐咗半年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話手足唔係condom<br />\n幫推大家關注啦"},{"pid":"d3aaddcf3a973dddec354c3bf6a08abc4f1433cd","tid":1780352,"uid":236124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2cb8dd7a504eb9f0dafe89d49e4dbe5f7d589e6","tid":1780352,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"朝早個個買飯團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:05:41.000Z","msg":"我記得有人求哮喘藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4850a8cf8033f49da432c91cc9f05d2cd75a16e","tid":1780352,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T10:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}